Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.98,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻譯：梅子 熊貓 校對：小白 時間：貓 後期：Waltz 壓制：Waltz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜 好鹹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜 好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:33.49,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday　言葉がたりなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:33.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日 言語不足以表達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:43.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すれ違ったとしても やめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:43.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使詞不達意 也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:50.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとわかりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:50.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:01:04.04,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時にひとりになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:01:04.04,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時 想一人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:15.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅をしても心は埋まらない そして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:15.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使旅行 內心的空虛也無法填補
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:20.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大切な人に気づくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:20.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我意識到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:24.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:24.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每時每刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:31.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　うまくいくとは限らない毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:31.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些有點小挫折的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你微笑面對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:45.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たったひとことがどれほど嬉しかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:45.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多麼令我開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとずっと覚えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至今日我也無法忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買了惠喜歡的高菜飯團哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屜野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑澤君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出版社說聯繫不到北川了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲門也不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎 北川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說給我聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 開門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多餘的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎樣都與你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我裝朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受夠了被人利用被人嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我好的時候裝朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都會背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不需要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一個人呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如剛才北川所說 有人就喜歡一個人呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人總是會背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友只會讓你受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是所有人都這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有人會想幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想著你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看看周圍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼關著自己不會有任何改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣是在傷害擔心你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我太軟弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你孤單了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠現在為什麼傷心我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你說給我聽我可能也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽也很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱怨也好 向我發火也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了讓大家高興做了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再努力 也不被重視
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家沒有一個人需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人怎麼想有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠從小時候開始就很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也被很多人認識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是真實的 這樣不就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自己毀掉這些努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得惠是所有人裡最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 惠就是惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己覺得自己最棒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直在你身邊支持你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠個子好高真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最醜才站在最後邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他們說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 果然很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要再自信一點啦 惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼時候都在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直聽著我說的話的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡放下一塊大石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(惠 收   媽媽)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…能接受這樣的自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有所改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的心會傷害別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(區區一個低水準讀模 別拽了)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我要為至今做的蠢事付出的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙根本就不在乎桃子你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了桃子才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒被她怎麼樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只是嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 別管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人為什麼會越陷越深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿著我的桌子幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在幫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把它搬進教室去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我實在看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠是個很溫柔的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我看不下去這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的那個惠並不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我只是為了好辦事 才對你好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但我只記得惠對我好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時常會帶我出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算惠你說這不是你所謂的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不討厭惠你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這樣的事也沒什麼的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有比這更過分的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已習慣這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 剛剛對你這麼凶 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不會再演繹那個虛假的惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我知道了 撒謊只會傷害自己和他人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不用再看別人臉色行事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用再結識那麼多不交心的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要演繹真實的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(283,100)}收藏夾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(176,139)}【第一】dessert讀者板塊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(204,250)}青年書刊版塊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要刪除1條收藏夾的內容嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  否
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(227,142)}東京風尚新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(236,198)}青年書刊版塊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 你把頭髮剪掉了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想換髮型 但沒那個勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在網上被讀者說了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼不好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總在意這些 就沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就永遠都做不了自己想做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種背後的流言蜚語 用不著這麼在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打工的時間延長了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 季節交替
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留下一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到了呢 夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼傻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅你去邀請人家也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千春 可以下班了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏日祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千春和誰一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 千春有男朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幹嘛不和我說啊 太見外了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭就是今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美給我來消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 今天去夏日祭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去的人…三點在商店街的標誌物前？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 剛剛在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想大家一起去 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海和北川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪麻美你老這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然嘴上這麼說 但你不也精心打扮了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像人妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛子醬好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美 吃巧克力香蕉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個都很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 要從哪個開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是也穿浴衣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅只要和平時一樣就足夠可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 在大家面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事呀 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱的天氣裡你們還這麼黏糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 你想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五平餅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我家養了貓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是把魚撈出來就夠開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國熱狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 還能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美 你吃太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回去休息下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等看煙花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要等很長時間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腳累得快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太難看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息會兒回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太死撐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 你去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你手機沒有聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幫你穿戴 火急火燎地回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估計著你要去夏日祭 所以幫你準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才已經去過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 還麻煩你特意準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年你不是一個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 已經和大和…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身打扮是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美地穿上浴衣 再畫個妝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在這種日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地當次女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意付出多少努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽只能幫梅做這些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 正式開始煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 正式開始煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(神社見)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去不去夏祭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上熟人怪麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…已經跟你遇上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要跟你一起看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花大會要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮亂糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得化了妝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花大會結束了 感謝觀賞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 這時候怎麼會想起這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人的手很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校裡不順心的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會覺得他們在對我說「會保護你的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都回去了又突然把你叫出來 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是覺得你現在超可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽給我準備了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就穿好過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然煙花大會結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想 無論如何也要讓大和看到這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了 這麼無聊的理由叫你出來 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
